sentences: DJ Jean (born Jean Engelaar, 7 May 1968) is a Dutch disc jockey.
He has been an influential figure in the electronic music scene since the early 1990s.
During the early 90's he had a Friday night residency is at club iT in Amsterdam, before it burned down.
He is prolific, and releases three or more compilation compact discs per year.
DJ Jean has performed all over the world, but now plays mostly in the Netherlands.
He now hosts a radioshow at Dutch radiostation Slam!FM, every Friday and Saturday night called DJ Jean @ work.
